commit.message: Gets directions and calculates remaining distance and required speed
Made locations searchable and shows path to location when found.
Added functions for getting directions from string destination
Added convertors for both LatLng types
Calculated relative distance for each waypoint along the route
Uses DirectionService to get path waypoints Asynchronously
DirectionsService now uses HTTP api call and calls a Callback when done
MainActivity finds directions/path from current location to Temple University
Added Gradle config files to repo
